        "subject": "LU-2271 tests: recovery-small test 10 to ensure reconnect",
        "message": "LU-2271 tests: recovery-small test 10 to ensure reconnect\n\nrecovery-small tet 10 might manage to get disconnected from more\nthan just MDS, but also OSTs, yet it does nothing to ensure\nit reconnects to all OSTs when it is finished. As the result\nthe next test being run fails when it tries to touch a disconnected OST\n(like first multiop in test 11 or 12 failing)\n\nChange-Id: I8961955ad3ecfbb2691a165cfc9580b30a9fe4b1\nSigned-off-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\n"
